---
title: Cheesy Chipotle-BBQ Tofu Bowls with Sweet Pepper Rice and Cucumber Salsa
description: This dairy- free vegetarian meal pops with saucy sweet and smoky flavours. Topped with plant-based mozzarella cheese, this recipe proves how delicious plant-based meals can be!
